.content
  div(id='meshleholm-carousel', class='carousel slide', data-ride='carousel', meshleholm-carousel)
  //-  ol.carousel-indicators
      li(data-target='#meshleholm-carousel', data-slide-to='{{ $index }}', ng-class="{'active': $index == 0, '': $index != 0}", ng-repeat='banner in banners')

    .carousel-inner
      div(ng-class="{'item active': $index == 0, 'item': $index != 0}", ng-repeat='banner in banners')
        img(ng-src='{{ banner.image }}', alt='{{ banner.text }}', style='width: 100%;')
        div(class='carousel-caption')
          h2(style='text-shadow: 0px 2px 3px #000;') {{ banner.header }}
          p.lead(style='text-shadow: 0px 2px 3px #000;') {{ banner.text }}
          p
            a(class='btn btn-lg btn-default', type='button', href='/join') Join Us
  //-
    a(class='left carousel-control', href='', ng-click='carouselPrev()', data-slide='prev')
      span(class='glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left')
    a(class='right carousel-control', href='', ng-click='carouselNext()', data-slide='next')
      span(class='glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right')

  .container
    .row
      .col-md-6
        h2 What is a Meshlocal?
        p
          | A Meshlocal is a local meshnet which runs CJDNS as its network protocol.
          | The dream is to create a decentralized community based network, a meshnet, and replace the centralized Internet.
      .col-md-6
        h2 Cjdns?
        p
          | From 
          a(href='http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cjdns') Wikipedia
          | , "Cjdns is a networking protocol, a system of digital rules for message exchange between computers. The philosophy behind cjdns is that networks should be easy to set up, protocols should scale up smoothly and security should be ubiquitous."

  include ../layout/footer
